tools.name: getWnbaScoreboard
tools.description: Get WNBA scoreboard for a specific date. Optional: dates (YYYYMMDD), limit (number)

tools.name: getWnbaGameBoxScore
tools.description: Get detailed box score for a specific WNBA game. Requires game_id parameter.

tools.name: getWnbaTeams
tools.description: Get all WNBA teams with basic information

tools.name: getWnbaTeamSchedule
tools.description: Get full season schedule for a specific WNBA team. Requires team_id parameter.

tools.name: getWnbaUpcomingGames
tools.description: Get upcoming WNBA games for the next N days. Optional: days (default 7)
